data.body:
This pull request converts the entire source to the javadoc comment style. This includes new-style license headers.
A new documentation comment looks like:

``` c++
/**
 * This is a brief description.  This is the long description, it contains
 * information about the method.
 */
void actual_method() {
// ...
}
```

 Additionally all trailing whitespace is removed, and all files were modified to contain exactly one newline at their end.
